view - package view

Abstract class for the controllers used for the common parts of them.

ViewCreator - Class in view

ViewHandler - Class in view
The class is used to set or initialize different views and controllers.

viewmodel - package viewmodel
 
ViewModelFactory - Class in viewmodel
The class is used to store, to construct and to obtain always the same objects of the ViewModel that the system needs.
ViewModelFactory(Model) - Constructor for class viewmodel.ViewModelFactory
One-argument constructor which initializes all the ViewModel objects.
ViewState - Class in viewmodel
The class represents the State of the views, storing the information needed to display the details of users, offers or renting deals.
